<h3>What is co-washing?</h3>
<p>Co-washing or conditioner washing is a method of washing your hair with a conditioner designed to cleanse. This process gently rids hair of dirt, excess oils, and product build-up without the use of sulfate detergents that can strip hair and cause damage. This leaves hair healthy, shiny, and more manageable.</p>
