<h3 class="p1"><span class="s1"><span>Why should I make the switch from shampoo?</span></span></h3>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1"><span>Most shampoos contain harsh detergents that strip hair of the natural, beneficial oils that protect, moisturize, and add shine.</span><span class="Apple-converted-space"> <span> </span></span><span>This leads to a flaky scalp and brittle strands.</span><span class="Apple-converted-space"> <span> </span></span><span>To add back the health that shampoo has washed away, conventional haircare regimens have us hooked on conditioner. That’s TWO products for ONE purpose: cleansing hair without drying it out.</span></span></p>
