<p class="p1"><span class="s1"><span>No, our Bio-Cleansing Conditioner gently washes away dirt and excess oil. Over time, co-washing will actually help balance your scalp’s oil production to its ideal state. If you feel your hair is getting heavy or limp with excess oil or buildup, you may be using too much product per wash or be in need of a deep cleanse. You can “reset” your hair and scalp using our Anti-Residue Cleanse &amp; Hydrating Masque without undoing all of the great benefits our Bio-Cleansing Conditioner has done.</span></span></p>
